name: 2024 12th International Conference on Biological and Medical Sciences
content: Publication: Accepted and registered papers can be published in: 1\. International Journal of Engineering and Technology (IJET, ISBN: 1793-8236), which will be indexed by Inspec (IET), CNKI, Google Scholar, EBSCO, ProQuest, Crossref, etc. 2\. International Journal of Pharma Medicine and Biological Sciences (IJPMBS, ISSN: 2278-5221), which will be indexed by Embase (under Elsevier), CNKI, ProQuest, etc.
